{"tid":1645482,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"首爾同台被指遲到　BLACKPINK疑累碧咸呆等","createTime":"2019-10-11T01:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T18:35:48.000Z","uid":231132,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7e627a44ef47bcdf4ebc4a1e8993426167d7ffae","tid":1645482,"uid":231132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media5.orientaldaily.com.my/storage/resize_cache/images/uploads/news-cover/2019/OCT_2019/20191010/8.jpg/a256d010bbd08c5d36c274c618366b55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia5.orientaldaily.com.my%2Fstorage%2Fresize_cache%2Fimages%2Fuploads%2Fnews-cover%2F2019%2FOCT_2019%2F20191010%2F8.jpg%2Fa256d010bbd08c5d36c274c618366b55.jpg&h=6ddcb264&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國&ldquo;足球金童&rdquo;大衛碧咸（David Beckham）近日赴韓國首爾參加活動，9日出席品牌70週年活動。 不過本來預計同台的韓國女團BLACKPINK被指出遲到20分鐘，讓大衛碧咸和現場媒體乾等，韓媒更是氣到打算集體走人。<br />\n<br />\n大衛碧咸8日抵達首爾，並於9日出席品牌活動，並與當地粉絲見面。 為了配上&ldquo;國際巨星&rdquo;，品牌也邀到在歐美極具知名度的女團BLACKPINK出席，與大衛碧咸同台。 大衛碧咸穿著黃色夾克現身，並親切對現場粉絲打招呼，不過卻也被發現似乎在現場空等，場面一度尷尬。.<br />\n<img src=\"https://media5.orientaldaily.com.my/images/uploads/news/2019/OCT_2019/20191010/EGaUixJUcAAoW9E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia5.orientaldaily.com.my%2Fimages%2Fuploads%2Fnews%2F2019%2FOCT_2019%2F20191010%2FEGaUixJUcAAoW9E.jpg&h=68ad0728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據韓媒報導，大衛碧咸和BLACKPINK原定同台，但<br />\nBLACKPINK遲到20分鐘，讓大衛碧咸和媒體們乾等，台上的訪談環節更是延遲開始，韓媒因此相當不悅， 甚至氣到要集體走人。<br />\n<br />\n 儘管大衛碧咸並未露出不悅表情，也表示好友詹姆斯柯登（James Corden）嫉妒自己可以見到BLACKPINK。 但遲到新聞曝光後，還是立刻衝上韓網熱門話題，留言更是戰成一片。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media5.orientaldaily.com.my/images/uploads/news/2019/OCT_2019/20191010/EGaUfRJWkAECBWB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia5.orientaldaily.com.my%2Fimages%2Fuploads%2Fnews%2F2019%2FOCT_2019%2F20191010%2FEGaUfRJWkAECBWB.jpg&h=c9e1dea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過BLACKPINK粉絲也跳出來為偶像解釋，表示她們一早就抵達現場並在後台等待，且活動本來就安排大衛碧咸的單獨現身，以及與BLACKPINK一起上台兩個環節，並非是&ldquo;讓碧咸等20分鐘&rdquo;。 粉絲也拿出影片表示，大衛碧咸台下還友善的與BLACKPINK成員一一擁抱問候，並不像是等待後而生氣的模樣，心疼偶像被誤會。"},{"pid":"6fe25d52c2d6471d54b314c72ed20e50bf1e49e5","tid":1645482,"uid":27416,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:56:07.000Z","msg":"留言邊有戰成一片<br />\n群屌喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac86c71083eaaf137cb4f04a714b680f29395fba","tid":1645482,"uid":152123,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:57:27.000Z","msg":"她們一早就抵達現場並在後台等待<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"27b4976d0f3d0de9983d242c925e73d20f308def","tid":1645482,"uid":19217,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:00:23.000Z","msg":"碧咸又幾好笑容喎"},{"pid":"74477cf1b76341125d8b3b6e69bb5fb9a0286628","tid":1645482,"uid":117802,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:11:26.000Z","msg":"粉絲也拿出影片表示，大衛碧咸台下還友善的與BLACKPINK成員一一擁抱問候，並不像是等待後而生氣的模樣，心疼偶像被誤會。<br />\n<br />\n因為咸爺好人同有禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5405bd0deb069845d12ade3a8755155d71faaf86","tid":1645482,"uid":89931,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ac86c71083eaaf137cb4f04a714b680f29395fba","tid":1645482,"uid":152123,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:57:27.000Z","msg":"她們一早就抵達現場並在後台等待<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:14:16.000Z","msg":"BLACKPINK粉絲也跳出來為偶像解釋，表示她們一早就抵達現場並在後台等待<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd58da2c578b9165aeb062a0d1fad2580aa6828","tid":1645482,"uid":19209,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:16:23.000Z","msg":"幾多人想佢地死 LOL"},{"pid":"69632ca141521d65ad4ee8bdbd451b2a23d79f9a","tid":1645482,"uid":40520,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:52:04.000Z","msg":"大會主辦已證實係佢地遲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e88c71724e5f45169